# Debug build after changes

After completing any task that modifies code, assets, or build config in this repo, run:

```bash
./build_debug.sh
```

Do this before finishing the response, even for small fixes. If the build fails, fix the errors and rebuild until it succeeds.

Report the APK paths from `out/` when a build was run (Play Store and Standalone variants).
